text: Natalia Karpenkova (born 1 February 1970) is a Belarusian trampoline gymnast. She competed in the women's trampoline event at the 2000 Summer Olympics and various Trampoline World Championships. ==Career statistics== ===Trampoline World Championships=== {| class="wikitable" |- !
